32#ifndef _COMPAT_OPENSOLARIS_SYS_CYCLIC_H_
33#define _COMPAT_OPENSOLARIS_SYS_CYCLIC_H_
34
35#ifndef _KERNEL
36typedef void cpu_t;
37#endif
38
39
40#ifndef _ASM
41#include <sys/time.h>
42#include <sys/cpuvar.h>
43#include <sys/cpupart.h>
44#endif /* !_ASM */
45
46#define CY_LOW_LEVEL 0
47#define CY_LOCK_LEVEL 1
48#define CY_HIGH_LEVEL 2
49#define CY_SOFT_LEVELS 2
50#define CY_LEVELS 3
51
52#ifndef _ASM
53
54typedef uintptr_t cyclic_id_t;
55typedef int cyc_index_t;
56typedef uint16_t cyc_level_t;
57typedef void (*cyc_func_t)(void *);
58typedef void *cyb_arg_t;
59
60#define CYCLIC_NONE ((cyclic_id_t)0)
61
62typedef struct cyc_handler {
63 cyc_func_t cyh_func;
64 void *cyh_arg;
65 cyc_level_t cyh_level;
66} cyc_handler_t;
67
68typedef struct cyc_time {
69 hrtime_t cyt_when;
70 hrtime_t cyt_interval;
71} cyc_time_t;
72
73typedef struct cyc_omni_handler {
74 void (*cyo_online)(void *, cpu_t *, cyc_handler_t *, cyc_time_t *);
75 void (*cyo_offline)(void *, cpu_t *, void *);
76 void *cyo_arg;
77} cyc_omni_handler_t;
78
79#define CY_INFINITY INT64_MAX
80
81#ifdef _KERNEL
82
83cyclic_id_t cyclic_add(cyc_handler_t *, cyc_time_t *);
84cyclic_id_t cyclic_add_omni(cyc_omni_handler_t *);
85void cyclic_remove(cyclic_id_t);
86int cyclic_reprogram(cyclic_id_t, hrtime_t);
87
88#endif /* _KERNEL */
89
90#endif /* !_ASM */
91
92#endif
